&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LOS-ANGELES-PROJECT-LOS-ANGELES-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8391&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LOS-ANGELES-PROJECT-LOS-ANGELES-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LOS ANGELES- PROJECT LOS ANGELES- OFFER LOGO&quot; width=&quot;181&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Located in the former location of The Roxy nightclub in Hollywood, Project Club LA is set in a dramatically designed 8500 square foot space, with the goal of leaving guests as much in awe as feeling welcomed. From the large dancefloor or 17 booths, guests are wowed by laser shows, projection screens and an intense sound system featuring open format music, encouraging existing 100% in the present. Dress code is upscale business casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Project LA by phone at +1-213-327-5166 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:alyssa@bng.la&quot;&gt;alyssa@bng.la&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any further instructions or details about reserving a table or bottle service will be provided at booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

